org.polarsys.chess.core.views

Class ViewDiagramAssociations

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.polarsys.chess.core.views.ViewDiagramAssociations

  • public class ViewDiagramAssociations
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of constants that defines the association between diagrams and design views and a mapping from Papyrus diagram names to UML names used internally by CHESS permissions.
